WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 18]

02:00.280 --> 02:01.460
I didn't expect you to come.

02:06.350 --> 02:07.130
I didn't either.

02:09.310 --> 02:09.850
You came

02:10.430 --> 02:11.540
to ask

02:12.430 --> 02:13.660
who you really are,

02:14.800 --> 02:15.170
right?

02:18.120 --> 02:18.570
No.

02:20.520 --> 02:21.380
I came to find you

02:22.630 --> 02:23.610
to ask

02:26.710 --> 02:27.540
where Wu Wangyan is.

02:31.280 --> 02:32.570
Even this Moon Summoning Pearl can't find her.

02:34.280 --> 02:35.450
Look at this Shilin Sect.

02:38.310 --> 02:39.260
Over a thousand years,

02:41.430 --> 02:43.340
there are too many power seals here.

02:44.080 --> 02:45.130
Even I can't undo them.

02:46.430 --> 02:47.290
And the Formless Moon

02:47.800 --> 02:48.940
has existed

02:49.190 --> 02:50.220
since Nuwa's time.

02:54.960 --> 02:55.410
There are

02:56.310 --> 02:57.780
also too many ancient seals there.

02:58.960 --> 03:00.340
A tiny Moon Summoning Pearl

03:01.030 --> 03:02.010
could hardly do anything.

03:11.750 --> 03:12.890
Greetings, Master Chi Wen.

03:25.800 --> 03:26.450
What's wrong?

03:27.840 --> 03:28.820
To our surprise, inside the Shilin Sect,

03:29.590 --> 03:30.940
there is a fragment of Jiu Ying's spirit.

03:32.680 --> 03:33.170
And

03:33.960 --> 03:36.010
it's hidden on one of us.

04:23.310 --> 04:24.100
So it's you!

04:33.070 --> 04:34.050
You must know

04:34.750 --> 04:35.930
what I want to discuss with you.

04:37.120 --> 04:37.660
Yes.

04:39.270 --> 04:40.050
This secret

04:41.680 --> 04:43.850
has long been kept in my heart.

04:48.430 --> 04:50.500
You were afraid the other members would find out,

04:51.160 --> 04:52.540
so you asked to see me alone.

04:54.000 --> 04:55.020
Stop pretending, Jiu Ying.

04:57.610 --> 04:59.600
Stop defiling her merciful face.

05:09.680 --> 05:11.110
You are braver

05:12.360 --> 05:13.300
than I thought.

05:15.310 --> 05:17.370
If I really carry a fragment of Jiu Ying's spirit,

05:18.240 --> 05:19.610
then doesn't that mean...

05:21.510 --> 05:22.700
Jiu Ying knows everything about me?

05:39.310 --> 05:40.700
Bai Ze's Eastern Purple Lightning

05:41.270 --> 05:42.490
can suppress evil spirits.

05:43.720 --> 05:44.410
Wear it,

05:45.390 --> 05:47.410
and it can temporarily suppress Jiu Ying's spirit.

06:19.070 --> 06:19.860
Thank you.

06:24.360 --> 06:24.730
Don't mention it.

06:28.510 --> 06:29.610
Aside from the two fragments

06:29.610 --> 06:30.700
inside the Oracle Stone,

06:31.120 --> 06:32.930
we've gathered all seventy-eight fragments

06:33.240 --> 06:34.660
in this world.

06:35.830 --> 06:36.490
I didn't expect

06:37.120 --> 06:38.140
the one

06:38.360 --> 06:39.730
that remained lost all this time

06:40.190 --> 06:41.080
would be on you.

06:41.680 --> 06:43.020
I'm going to the Formless Moon to save someone.

06:43.630 --> 06:44.910
Maybe we can go together.

06:45.600 --> 06:46.780
We can destroy the last two fragments

06:47.270 --> 06:47.900
in the Oracle Stone.

06:48.750 --> 06:50.000
The Oracle Stone is a sacred stone

06:50.000 --> 06:51.930
created by Pan Gu and Nuwa together.

06:52.480 --> 06:53.170
Ordinary power

06:53.600 --> 06:54.490
can hardly damage it.

06:55.190 --> 06:56.540
Only by gathering the Dragon Deity's Power

06:57.360 --> 06:57.900
might there be

06:58.430 --> 06:59.700
a chance to destroy it.

07:02.000 --> 07:02.980
What about Wu Wangyan?

07:04.270 --> 07:04.610
I promise you.

07:06.160 --> 07:07.410
She will be saved.

07:09.070 --> 07:09.490
And

07:10.870 --> 07:11.850
Lu Wuyi is there too.

07:13.430 --> 07:15.170
We're about to enter the Sacred Spring.

07:15.800 --> 07:17.900
Why did the Queen summon Wang alone?
[*Wang is Wu Wangyan]

07:20.630 --> 07:21.060
Hui,
[*Hui is Lu Wuyi]

07:22.000 --> 07:23.780
you're the closest to Wang.

07:24.680 --> 07:25.850
Do you know what's going on?

07:28.430 --> 07:29.290
I don't know.

07:30.310 --> 07:31.080
Wangyan...

07:31.560 --> 07:32.850
didn't tell me anything.

07:55.750 --> 07:57.020
It may be out of your reach

07:58.870 --> 08:00.490
to deal with me.

08:03.310 --> 08:04.900
I've been wondering

08:06.240 --> 08:08.660
why your memories were always fragmented

08:09.600 --> 08:11.050
every time we entered the Sacred Spring.

08:12.380 --> 08:13.530
Turns out

08:13.870 --> 08:15.500
you suspected me all along,

08:16.390 --> 08:18.060
and removed some memories

08:18.630 --> 08:19.630
you didn't want me

08:20.070 --> 08:21.140
and your sisters

08:21.160 --> 08:22.100
to know.

08:22.720 --> 08:23.170
Right?

08:24.520 --> 08:25.260
Yes.

08:27.600 --> 08:29.220
But tonight,

08:29.720 --> 08:31.870
if I share my memories with them,

08:32.920 --> 08:34.230
all of them will know

08:34.660 --> 08:37.030
that you are Jiu Ying.

08:39.440 --> 08:40.730
You won't get the chance.

08:53.390 --> 08:54.730
The Tenth Dragon Son

08:55.390 --> 08:58.420
can help you kill Chi Wen.

09:02.360 --> 09:03.610
You know too much.

09:05.120 --> 09:06.300
You deserve to die.

09:12.200 --> 09:13.420
Keep me alive...

09:14.790 --> 09:16.580
and I can help you.

09:17.270 --> 09:18.730
I am his weakness.

09:19.910 --> 09:22.850
He'll obey you for my sake...

09:23.030 --> 09:24.340
I need your help?

09:26.080 --> 09:27.100
Have you forgotten

09:29.080 --> 09:30.530
what I'm best at?

09:44.870 --> 09:46.530
When I wiped out the Flood Dragon clan,

09:47.270 --> 09:48.980
I transferred

09:49.000 --> 09:50.220
the spirit fragment in you

09:51.510 --> 09:53.530
into Wu Shiguang's body.

09:56.750 --> 09:57.420
No way...

09:58.750 --> 10:01.540
Then how did you appear in the Oracle Stone?

10:02.320 --> 10:03.770
The Oracle Stone

10:04.360 --> 10:06.100
has three fragments.

10:08.550 --> 10:09.180
Back then,

10:09.600 --> 10:10.540
one fragment was used

10:10.910 --> 10:12.870
to control you to slaughter the Flood Dragon clan.

10:13.640 --> 10:14.790
The rest remain

10:15.840 --> 10:17.010
in the Oracle Stone.

10:24.240 --> 10:26.190
You're right, though.

10:26.660 --> 10:27.460
Keeping you alive

10:28.670 --> 10:30.820
can indeed be his weakness.

10:55.440 --> 10:55.850
No.

10:57.000 --> 10:58.940
Get close to Wu Shiguang.

10:59.880 --> 11:01.900
Try to get his prayer beads

11:03.120 --> 11:04.250
and bring them to me.

11:09.360 --> 11:10.770
So you and the Dragon Deity

11:12.750 --> 11:14.180
have been plotting all along.

11:40.200 --> 11:41.580
I will find out the truth

11:41.950 --> 11:43.420
and prove Wangyan hasn't betrayed us.

11:44.030 --> 11:44.650
Wangyan,

11:44.750 --> 11:46.460
why are you

11:46.630 --> 11:48.300
so fragrant today?

11:48.600 --> 11:49.650
You deceived Wangyan,

11:50.030 --> 11:51.700
using her to do your work.

11:52.000 --> 11:53.490
What's your purpose exactly?

11:54.000 --> 11:55.010
When we go back

11:55.320 --> 11:56.770
and enter the Sacred Spring,

11:56.870 --> 11:58.060
your plan with Wangyan

11:58.600 --> 11:59.850
will be known by the Queen.

12:00.120 --> 12:01.130
Without memory sharing,

12:02.030 --> 12:03.420
would you tell your Queen?

12:46.440 --> 12:47.060
Wangyan.

12:53.600 --> 12:55.340
Everything I said to the Dragon Deity

12:55.360 --> 12:56.250
was a lie.

12:57.960 --> 12:59.580
I was just playing along

13:01.070 --> 13:03.580
to carry out the Queen's mission.

13:04.080 --> 13:04.730
Really?

13:20.360 --> 13:22.730
Greetings, Master.

13:38.630 --> 13:39.490
I'm sorry,

13:40.030 --> 13:40.770
Master.

13:44.550 --> 13:46.460
I ask to quit the Dragon-Slaying mission.

13:48.910 --> 13:49.490
See?

13:51.750 --> 13:52.730
The fated one

13:53.720 --> 13:55.300
can't escape fate after all.

13:57.200 --> 13:58.010
Master,

14:01.120 --> 14:02.180
what exactly does

14:05.200 --> 14:06.340
"fated one" mean?

14:07.900 --> 14:09.000
When the time comes,

14:09.960 --> 14:10.940
you'll understand.

14:14.630 --> 14:15.340
Where's Wangyan?

14:17.120 --> 14:17.940
Where did she go?

14:22.120 --> 14:22.770
She's...

14:24.840 --> 14:25.850
in quiet reflection.

14:36.390 --> 14:37.530
There's no moon tonight.

14:41.150 --> 14:42.220
The moon is always there,

14:42.960 --> 14:44.110
just hiding for now.

14:47.000 --> 14:49.240
The other moons are all bright and clear.

14:49.750 --> 14:51.340
Poets write verses

14:51.360 --> 14:52.310
praising them.

14:53.440 --> 14:54.340
Do you think

14:56.600 --> 14:58.460
that moon no one can see

15:00.720 --> 15:01.770
would feel sad?

15:03.030 --> 15:04.460
What other moons?

15:06.600 --> 15:07.850
There is only one moon,

15:08.670 --> 15:09.770
just in different phases.

15:10.790 --> 15:11.220
We...

15:12.670 --> 15:13.580
are one.

15:22.870 --> 15:23.460
Wangyan,

15:25.270 --> 15:26.420
if one day,

15:27.790 --> 15:29.130
no one can see me anymore,

15:31.120 --> 15:32.130
will you remember me?

15:33.320 --> 15:34.130
Silly,

15:36.440 --> 15:37.940
we'll be together forever.

15:38.420 --> 15:41.180
♪How should this story be told♪

15:41.380 --> 15:46.180
♪So boiling water turns so cold?♪

15:46.300 --> 15:49.140
♪The years run wild, yet drift along♪

15:49.380 --> 15:54.340
♪Close my eyes, hear the bustling throng♪

15:55.100 --> 15:57.140
♪In the light, the great tree♪

15:57.540 --> 16:02.460
♪Sways gently, watching the mortal world burn bright♪

16:03.180 --> 16:04.340
♪Oh, little blade of grass♪

16:05.020 --> 16:08.660
♪I want to go somewhere else♪

16:10.340 --> 16:12.980
♪How do you measure memory♪

16:13.260 --> 16:18.100
♪To cut the past into clothes to wear?♪

16:18.260 --> 16:20.940
♪The little blade of grass, eyes brimming with tears♪

16:21.260 --> 16:26.300
♪Holds fallen leaves and grieves♪

16:27.060 --> 16:29.020
♪Summer heat fades into autumn's chill♪

16:29.260 --> 16:30.860
♪Winter snow falls in haste...♪

16:33.630 --> 16:34.180
Wuyi,

16:35.630 --> 16:36.370
I'm sorry...

16:36.940 --> 16:40.780
♪The passing years are nothing more than an evening glow...♪

16:43.320 --> 16:43.980
I lied to you.

16:45.390 --> 16:46.370
No need to apologize.

16:49.910 --> 16:50.860
I lied to you too.

16:53.840 --> 16:55.300
The Queen had me watch you.

16:57.000 --> 16:58.690
I know about your partnership

16:59.870 --> 17:00.730
with Ji Ling.

17:07.320 --> 17:08.770
So you told the Queen?

17:15.720 --> 17:16.770
Do you hate me?

17:17.550 --> 17:17.980
No.

17:21.350 --> 17:22.490
I could never hate you.

17:27.350 --> 17:28.980
Aren't you going to ask why I'm here?

17:30.270 --> 17:31.700
If the Queen sent me to kill you,

17:32.750 --> 17:33.660
you wouldn't hate me?

17:39.310 --> 17:39.900
No.

17:41.790 --> 17:43.420
If I die by your hand,

17:44.790 --> 17:45.980
at least it wouldn't hurt.

17:46.420 --> 17:48.980
♪The great tree softly hums♪

17:49.260 --> 17:54.140
♪Now near, now far, scattered by the wind♪

17:54.300 --> 17:57.100
♪The grass stands on tiptoes♪

17:57.340 --> 18:02.740
♪The sky's too high and far, afraid it won't hear♪

18:03.180 --> 18:04.740
♪You always said...♪

18:04.750 --> 18:05.570
Wu Wangyan...

18:05.580 --> 18:07.020
♪This world is full of wonder...♪

18:08.270 --> 18:09.770
What do you really want?

18:11.260 --> 18:12.540
♪But I only wish...♪

18:13.480 --> 18:14.330
I don't know.

18:16.550 --> 18:17.600
But I know

18:19.200 --> 18:20.250
what I don't want.

18:21.350 --> 18:22.420
Not even your life?

18:23.640 --> 18:25.040
Not even your own life?

18:27.380 --> 18:30.220
♪Lost in the heavy mist♪

18:30.340 --> 18:34.140
♪Found again in dewdrops...♪

18:37.480 --> 18:38.860
I don't want my hands

18:38.920 --> 18:40.220
to be forever stained with blood.

18:42.070 --> 18:43.860
I don't want Jiu Ying to keep controlling me,

18:44.920 --> 18:47.010
stirring up killing and hatred in this world.

18:49.070 --> 18:50.460
I don't want to be a moon...

18:51.220 --> 18:54.780
♪Little grass, O little grass...♪

18:54.790 --> 18:56.380
that only lights up mass graves.

18:59.300 --> 19:06.060
♪I know your dreams will bloom at last♪

19:06.780 --> 19:10.540
♪Little grass, O little grass♪

19:10.740 --> 19:14.580
♪Be brave enough to chase the vast...♪

19:18.350 --> 19:18.940
Do it.

19:22.020 --> 19:26.580
♪Great tree, O great tree♪

19:26.740 --> 19:31.700
♪Through snow and storm, you bend but breathe♪

19:40.720 --> 19:41.320
Wuyi,

19:41.680 --> 19:42.530
what's wrong?

19:46.790 --> 19:47.460
Wangyan...

19:50.440 --> 19:51.940
I never told the Queen.

19:53.510 --> 19:54.980
I would never betray you.

19:56.240 --> 19:57.730
I came to ask you...

20:00.070 --> 20:01.290
if you still remember...

20:04.790 --> 20:06.730
the words you once said to me.

20:10.240 --> 20:11.330
I have never forgotten.

20:11.790 --> 20:13.460
Then why did you leave me behind

20:14.640 --> 20:15.490
and go alone?

20:19.880 --> 20:20.900
Because this path...

20:24.000 --> 20:24.810
is too dangerous.

20:28.030 --> 20:29.290
I didn't want you to walk it.

20:31.070 --> 20:32.250
Because my enemy

20:33.640 --> 20:34.420
is too terrifying.

20:35.440 --> 20:36.620
So I couldn't tell you.

20:39.160 --> 20:40.330
The danger...

20:45.030 --> 20:46.140
the truth...

20:47.920 --> 20:49.050
even my guilt toward you...

20:51.220 --> 20:52.420
none of it could be said.

20:55.510 --> 20:56.180
Enemy?

20:58.810 --> 20:59.750
Danger?

21:01.070 --> 21:02.650
You mean...

21:03.880 --> 21:04.860
the Queen?

21:07.590 --> 21:08.140
The Queen...

21:10.000 --> 21:11.180
is Jiu Ying.

21:14.030 --> 21:15.250
When the real Queen passed,

21:16.440 --> 21:18.290
her power had faded.

21:19.720 --> 21:21.890
We missed her so much,

21:23.110 --> 21:25.090
so when Jiu Ying wore her skin

21:25.090 --> 21:26.950
and showed up,

21:28.030 --> 21:29.770
we deceived ourselves

21:30.830 --> 21:32.980
into believing she had gained

21:34.160 --> 21:36.530
the power of endless rebirth like us.

21:57.750 --> 21:58.940
He impersonated the Queen,

21:59.640 --> 22:01.250
faking the Oracle Stone's prophecy,

22:02.070 --> 22:03.860
ordering us to sow killing and hatred

22:03.880 --> 22:04.740
in this world.

22:05.510 --> 22:07.460
He called it the balance of the world,

22:08.400 --> 22:09.730
and we believed it without question.

22:11.000 --> 22:12.570
But Xiaowei saw through him.

22:16.320 --> 22:17.060
Wang,

22:18.350 --> 22:19.520
she is no longer

22:19.520 --> 22:21.130
the kind Queen we knew.

22:21.880 --> 22:22.910
The Formless Moon

22:23.550 --> 22:25.920
is now filled with only cruelty and slaughter.

22:28.000 --> 22:29.030
Let me go.

22:30.160 --> 22:30.980
You should find a way

22:31.970 --> 22:33.030
and escape too.

22:36.270 --> 22:37.600
Xiaowei is a traitor.

22:38.030 --> 22:38.940
Can her words

22:40.070 --> 22:41.190
be trusted?

22:41.830 --> 22:43.010
I am a traitor too.

22:44.160 --> 22:45.140
Then do you believe

22:46.400 --> 22:47.700
my words?

23:04.400 --> 23:05.560
Who dares trespass?

23:06.110 --> 23:07.380
Aren't you afraid of perishing?

23:09.550 --> 23:10.140
Dragon Deity?

23:11.920 --> 23:14.090
Since you know who I am,

23:15.310 --> 23:16.220
why don't you back off?

23:17.720 --> 23:19.250
The Formless Moon is beyond this world,

23:20.270 --> 23:21.900
not bound by its rules.

23:22.720 --> 23:24.180
We respect what you've done

23:24.200 --> 23:25.050
for all living things,

23:26.200 --> 23:27.730
but that doesn't mean we obey you.

23:28.830 --> 23:29.530
Master Dragon Deity,

23:30.550 --> 23:31.220
please leave.

23:32.680 --> 23:33.570
Where is Wu Wangyan?

23:34.510 --> 23:35.250
Let her out.

23:35.310 --> 23:35.660
How dare you!

23:36.400 --> 23:38.460
Moon spirit invoked, your radiance eternal,

23:38.480 --> 23:39.010
arise!

24:13.350 --> 24:14.380
By the fox's call,

24:15.270 --> 24:16.620
lend me your souls!

24:22.510 --> 24:23.250
Formless Moon members,

24:24.160 --> 24:24.860
come forth.

24:39.200 --> 24:41.220
Kneel before me.

24:45.510 --> 24:46.660
Obey me.

24:54.880 --> 24:55.770
You guys go save them.

24:57.480 --> 24:58.290
I'll handle things here.

25:02.200 --> 25:02.730
Wu Wangyan?

25:03.960 --> 25:04.420
Wu Wangyan!

25:15.640 --> 25:16.380
I told you,

25:17.830 --> 25:18.810
I would find you.

25:24.480 --> 25:25.380
How did you know

25:25.400 --> 25:26.490
where the Formless Moon is?

25:27.310 --> 25:28.050
Chi Wen knows.

25:37.400 --> 25:38.140
He's here too?

25:39.830 --> 25:40.250
Yes.

25:46.790 --> 25:47.570
I want to know

25:49.310 --> 25:50.570
who I really am.

25:53.510 --> 25:54.660
Knowing who you can be

25:55.440 --> 25:56.620
is more important

25:57.830 --> 25:58.330
than that.

26:00.270 --> 26:01.050
All memories

26:02.160 --> 26:03.180
are paths you've walked,

26:04.310 --> 26:05.090
a burden

26:06.200 --> 26:07.730
not worth turning back to walk again.

26:08.830 --> 26:09.460
Forward

26:10.350 --> 26:11.290
is the way to go.

26:12.590 --> 26:13.980
But if I don't know who I am,

26:16.550 --> 26:18.640
I don't know which way to go.

26:19.160 --> 26:20.840
If you really want to know it,

26:21.270 --> 26:22.730
just go ask that butterfly demon.

26:24.270 --> 26:25.290
I'm teaching him reason,

26:26.070 --> 26:27.090
but you're teaching him to break the rules!

26:28.160 --> 26:29.380
Master Chi Wen strictly forbids

26:30.000 --> 26:31.570
anyone to approach the butterfly demon.

26:33.270 --> 26:34.220
Why be so obedient?

26:34.920 --> 26:35.290
Li Jie,

26:35.750 --> 26:37.050
while Master is away,

26:37.440 --> 26:38.570
sneak in

26:38.750 --> 26:39.380
and find out.

26:40.000 --> 26:40.420
What do you say?

27:18.940 --> 27:20.100
Do you really think

27:20.680 --> 27:22.860
you can easily take Wu Wangyan away?

27:25.200 --> 27:25.980
Do you really think

27:27.310 --> 27:28.660
I'm here to save Wu Wangyan?

27:37.420 --> 27:38.870
Dragon hearts as one,

27:40.400 --> 27:41.330
all to source return,

27:43.400 --> 27:45.530
all barriers break!

27:59.650 --> 28:00.610
It worked!

28:34.350 --> 28:35.500
Even the Dragon Deity's Power

28:36.590 --> 28:38.180
can't break Jiu Ying's seal.

28:41.110 --> 28:42.290
Jiu Ying has been absorbing

28:42.310 --> 28:43.510
the Oracle Stone's power,

28:43.640 --> 28:44.620
growing stronger.

28:45.920 --> 28:47.060
And Wu Shiguang only has

28:47.060 --> 28:48.700
two pieces of the Dragon Deity's Power.

28:49.310 --> 28:50.220
It's not enough.

28:53.880 --> 28:54.940
I also have one piece inside me.

28:57.270 --> 28:57.620
No!

28:58.240 --> 29:00.290
If you give it up, you'll die.

29:01.200 --> 29:02.380
Xiaowei and Wu Zhiqi died

29:02.960 --> 29:03.770
because Yuan Wuhuo

29:03.790 --> 29:05.330
forcibly took their Dragon Deity's Power

29:06.240 --> 29:07.570
and damaged their spiritual veins.

29:08.400 --> 29:09.940
If I give mine willingly,

29:10.350 --> 29:11.140
I'll be fine.

29:12.070 --> 29:13.700
Master Chi Wen saved me

29:14.960 --> 29:15.660
with this power

29:16.440 --> 29:17.770
that was never mine.

29:18.750 --> 29:19.570
Returning it

29:20.720 --> 29:21.860
is only right.

29:24.720 --> 29:25.620
Dragon hearts as one,

29:26.440 --> 29:27.250
all to source return,

29:28.200 --> 29:29.680
all barriers break!

30:13.920 --> 30:14.940
From now on,

30:15.480 --> 30:16.620
you are neither demon

30:16.880 --> 30:17.860
nor human.

30:19.160 --> 30:20.140
In this world,

30:20.160 --> 30:21.570
you will be a unique existence

30:22.310 --> 30:24.220
and also the loneliest of its kind.

30:25.400 --> 30:26.530
From this moment,

30:27.200 --> 30:29.090
you are Chi Wen,

30:29.680 --> 30:31.730
the last Dragon Deity in this world.

30:32.590 --> 30:36.490
So how long must I deceive the world?

30:38.240 --> 30:39.850
Until the Dragon's tenth son

30:39.850 --> 30:41.380
awakens as a true dragon,

30:41.880 --> 30:44.330
your duty will be done.

30:47.160 --> 30:48.250
I didn't come here

30:49.160 --> 30:50.290
to be your enemy,

30:51.550 --> 30:52.860
but to seek cooperation.

30:56.310 --> 30:57.220
Don't trust me?

30:59.160 --> 31:00.250
If I hadn't told you

31:00.270 --> 31:01.250
about Wu Wangyan's betrayal

31:01.830 --> 31:03.490
and the Taotie artifact,

31:04.160 --> 31:05.250
you might still be dancing

31:05.720 --> 31:06.860
in her palm

31:06.880 --> 31:07.940
even now.

31:08.680 --> 31:10.180
Since she has betrayed you,

31:10.920 --> 31:11.860
all her memories

31:12.160 --> 31:13.050
are stored

31:13.070 --> 31:14.490
inside the Taotie artifact.

31:14.920 --> 31:15.620
If you don't believe me,

31:17.750 --> 31:18.940
you can see for yourself.

31:24.000 --> 31:25.620
Wu Wangyan is pitiful.

31:26.720 --> 31:28.550
She trusted you, helped you,

31:29.400 --> 31:30.570
but never knew

31:31.160 --> 31:32.530
she was just a pawn in your game.

31:33.680 --> 31:34.570
For great goals,

31:35.550 --> 31:36.380
small costs are nothing.

31:38.000 --> 31:38.980
But you're pitiful too.

31:41.440 --> 31:43.470
You're just a pawn in Chi Wen's game.

31:44.880 --> 31:45.290
That's right.

31:47.990 --> 31:50.310
Chi Wen wants me to wait for the tenth son,

31:51.400 --> 31:53.980
then hand over the Dragon Deity's throne

31:54.070 --> 31:54.900
I worked so hard to build.

31:57.510 --> 31:59.330
All those centuries of suffering

32:01.640 --> 32:03.090
would be a joke then?

32:04.560 --> 32:05.320
So...

32:07.830 --> 32:08.290
Jiu Ying,

32:09.440 --> 32:10.530
we should work together.

32:11.720 --> 32:12.660
My goal

32:13.480 --> 32:14.420
aligns with yours:

32:16.200 --> 32:17.010
to slay the dragon deity.

32:19.550 --> 32:21.220
Even if Chi Wen dies,

32:22.480 --> 32:23.570
there's still the tenth son.

32:25.110 --> 32:26.570
How could a false deity like you

32:27.290 --> 32:27.980
ever take the throne?

32:31.960 --> 32:34.030
I intended to seize the Dragon Deity's Power

32:34.270 --> 32:35.770
to stop Wu Shiguang from rising.

32:36.480 --> 32:38.140
But Yuan Wuhuo meddled,

32:38.960 --> 32:40.060
and things went awry,

32:40.510 --> 32:42.380
unexpectedly helping Wu Shiguang.

32:44.000 --> 32:45.700
Since he's destined to be a dragon,

32:46.720 --> 32:48.180
let him do the slaying.

32:49.240 --> 32:49.730
Besides,

32:50.720 --> 32:51.900
doesn't this play right

32:52.310 --> 32:53.980
into the self-protection

32:54.510 --> 32:56.420
they set up out of fear?

32:58.680 --> 33:00.090
Only the Dragon Deity's Power

33:01.030 --> 33:02.330
can kill a dragon deity.

33:04.680 --> 33:05.660
And that

33:07.200 --> 33:08.490
is such a grave crime

33:11.000 --> 33:11.810
that the slayer, too,

33:12.790 --> 33:14.250
will be consumed by its curse.

33:16.350 --> 33:17.380
Then the throne

33:19.590 --> 33:21.050
will be mine forever.

33:28.270 --> 33:29.380
What are you waiting for?

33:30.270 --> 33:32.050
You've been trapped in Chi Wen's broken body

33:33.030 --> 33:33.770
for so many years.

33:34.440 --> 33:36.170
You should know

33:36.550 --> 33:37.440
I didn't lie.

33:38.400 --> 33:38.900
Isn't that right?

33:40.310 --> 33:41.770
The Dragon's tenth son...

33:45.240 --> 33:47.620
Only the Dragon Deity's Power can slay a dragon deity.

33:48.590 --> 33:50.570
So Jiu Ying will use the tenth son

33:50.590 --> 33:51.330
to kill me,

33:51.960 --> 33:53.090
so his true form

33:53.510 --> 33:56.010
can break free from my body.

33:59.640 --> 34:00.460
The Dragon's tenth son?

34:02.640 --> 34:03.490
Interesting.

34:08.310 --> 34:10.080
You also sent butterfly demons

34:10.510 --> 34:12.380
to seize the tenth son from the Dragon Abyss.

34:17.110 --> 34:17.740
That's right.

34:31.630 --> 34:33.940
That outer-world being, Xie Lingxi,

34:34.150 --> 34:35.260
is indeed something.

34:36.320 --> 34:37.010
However,

34:37.400 --> 34:38.380
he's too confident.

34:38.960 --> 34:39.900
He thought hiding the son

34:40.190 --> 34:41.530
among the flood dragons

34:41.880 --> 34:43.130
with scales and horns too

34:43.590 --> 34:45.470
would be safe enough

34:45.510 --> 34:46.650
to protect him.

34:48.070 --> 34:48.910
Too bad.

34:49.880 --> 34:51.530
I still found the tenth son.

34:53.670 --> 34:56.300
You had the Formless Moon pose as the Shilin Sect

34:56.630 --> 34:58.130
and slaughtered the Flood Dragon clan,

34:59.070 --> 35:00.610
making Xie Lingxi suspicious

35:01.000 --> 35:01.900
of the Shilin Sect,

35:02.840 --> 35:04.530
so he hid the son deeper.

35:05.590 --> 35:06.170
The tenth son

35:07.070 --> 35:09.010
vanished without a trace.

35:10.360 --> 35:11.130
Suspicion

35:12.880 --> 35:15.490
is the best weapon against the human heart.

35:16.510 --> 35:17.610
The Shilin Sect

35:17.800 --> 35:19.570
had no news of the tenth son,

35:20.110 --> 35:21.630
but I always knew

35:21.760 --> 35:22.900
where he was.

35:23.670 --> 35:25.390
That's because you planted

35:25.440 --> 35:26.980
a fragment of spirit inside him.

35:28.800 --> 35:32.380
But Wu Shiguang has grown up,

35:32.920 --> 35:34.300
yet he hasn't become a dragon,

35:34.320 --> 35:35.700
which made me suspicious.

35:36.670 --> 35:37.130
So,

35:38.070 --> 35:39.590
you sent the Six-Eyed Butterfly.

35:42.320 --> 35:42.940
Yes.

35:44.760 --> 35:46.270
I had him devour a person

35:48.840 --> 35:50.780
to obtain his consciousness and memories.

36:08.320 --> 36:09.090
I knew...

36:12.550 --> 36:13.740
you would come.

36:14.960 --> 36:15.570
Tell me,

36:17.280 --> 36:18.170
who exactly are you?

36:20.590 --> 36:21.940
I am you.

36:25.480 --> 36:26.210
And that person

36:27.670 --> 36:29.460
was the former hunter commander of the Shilin Sect,

36:30.000 --> 36:32.170
plagued by the Wasting Sickness

36:32.480 --> 36:33.940
and long missing,

36:36.280 --> 36:37.010
Yuan Wuhuo.

36:48.400 --> 36:49.380
You should be familiar with him.

36:53.590 --> 36:55.340
When I found Yuan Wuhuo,

36:56.360 --> 36:57.530
he was a decaying man

36:57.550 --> 36:58.860
waiting to die

36:58.960 --> 37:01.050
alone in a cave.

37:03.550 --> 37:04.780
Aging,

37:05.230 --> 37:06.980
gravely wounded beasts

37:07.320 --> 37:10.170
will all, in their final moments,

37:10.710 --> 37:12.610
go alone into hidden forests

37:12.630 --> 37:14.050
or deep caves.

37:15.960 --> 37:17.530
They don't want their own kind

37:17.550 --> 37:19.490
to witness their death.

37:20.920 --> 37:24.740
That is their final pride.

37:24.780 --> 37:30.460
♪One flower, one tree beside a grave♪

37:31.140 --> 37:36.900
♪Autumn hides the pain, but moon conveys♪

37:38.660 --> 37:44.700
♪Immortal world, the years in pain♪

37:45.060 --> 37:49.860
♪All sorrows fade in death's one wake♪

39:42.280 --> 39:42.820
Who are you?

39:43.550 --> 39:44.420
Where are you from?

39:46.960 --> 39:47.780
I don't remember.

39:49.280 --> 39:50.420
What do you remember?

39:52.670 --> 39:53.610
It seems...

39:55.320 --> 39:56.740
I have a younger brother.

39:58.360 --> 39:59.610
It seems...

40:01.230 --> 40:02.380
I need to find him.

40:28.590 --> 40:29.690
To my surprise,

40:30.070 --> 40:32.090
it took the Six-Eyed Butterfly decades

40:32.280 --> 40:34.050
to fully consume the consciousness and memories

40:34.150 --> 40:35.130
of Yuan Wuhuo.

40:35.920 --> 40:37.090
His will was unyielding,

40:37.920 --> 40:39.260
rare in this world.

40:40.960 --> 40:42.610
He truly was a stubborn man.

40:43.960 --> 40:45.200
Even the most stubborn one

40:45.840 --> 40:47.340
can't outlast time.

40:48.280 --> 40:49.920
The mortal lifespan

40:50.590 --> 40:52.440
is their greatest shackle.

40:53.480 --> 40:55.630
Yuan Wuhuo is no more.

40:56.670 --> 40:57.830
After that,

40:58.320 --> 40:59.570
the Six-Eyed Butterfly

40:59.590 --> 41:02.300
roamed the world in his form.

41:04.480 --> 41:07.040
When the Six-Eyed Butterfly returned to your side,

41:07.710 --> 41:09.960
you learned of the tenth son's secret.

41:10.780 --> 41:11.820
It's coming soon.

41:12.670 --> 41:13.740
Master Chi Wen entrusted

41:13.800 --> 41:15.820
the tenth son

41:15.820 --> 41:17.290
to a very capable person to raise.

41:17.920 --> 41:18.820
When he comes of age,

41:19.720 --> 41:21.060
he will come to you.

41:21.880 --> 41:22.880
When he comes of age,

41:23.790 --> 41:25.070
will he become a dragon?

41:26.670 --> 41:28.530
Like Master Chi Wen,

41:29.310 --> 41:30.630
majestic and powerful,

41:31.480 --> 41:32.300
soaring through the heavens?

41:33.470 --> 41:35.170
The tenth son is special.

41:36.030 --> 41:38.520
He was created from nine reverse scales.

41:39.000 --> 41:41.210
He needs four pieces of the Dragon Deity's Power

41:41.230 --> 41:42.690
to awaken and become a dragon.

41:43.480 --> 41:44.300
First, his scales form.

41:45.400 --> 41:46.420
Second, his claws grow.

41:47.480 --> 41:48.650
Third, his horns sprout.

41:50.470 --> 41:51.800
Fourth, his eyes ignite.

41:52.760 --> 41:54.480
You were eager to obtain the Dragon Deity's Power

41:54.670 --> 41:56.590
to enter Wu Shiguang's body,

41:57.070 --> 41:58.090
so you used the fragment of spirit

41:58.110 --> 41:59.530
planted within him.

42:00.400 --> 42:01.170
And subtly,

42:01.710 --> 42:03.570
you gave him hints,

42:03.880 --> 42:05.130
leading him to Luo'an City.

42:05.920 --> 42:07.170
Every step after that,

42:08.130 --> 42:09.680
it's hard to say

42:10.050 --> 42:12.080
whether it was Wu Shiguang's own will

42:13.110 --> 42:14.870
or your influence driving him.

42:17.030 --> 42:18.390
Everything you said is correct.

42:19.400 --> 42:20.870
But for your spirit fragment

42:21.230 --> 42:22.750
to fully control him,

42:23.920 --> 42:24.900
you still need to find

42:25.400 --> 42:27.080
the dark sides in his heart.

42:28.870 --> 42:30.850
Wu Shiguang is not weak-willed.

42:32.670 --> 42:33.690
After possessing him for so long,

42:34.720 --> 42:37.310
you've never found a way to break his will.

42:38.910 --> 42:40.070
Not before,

42:41.550 --> 42:43.080
but now I have.

42:44.360 --> 42:45.410
You mean Wu Wangyan?

42:48.830 --> 42:51.020
Nothing breaks a person's spirit

42:52.140 --> 42:55.570
more than losing what they love most.

42:56.400 --> 42:57.580
After all these years,

42:58.360 --> 42:59.420
you still don't understand

42:59.510 --> 43:00.720
the human heart enough.

43:02.080 --> 43:04.070
Wu Shiguang already knows about her role

43:04.070 --> 43:05.550
in slaughtering the Flood Dragon clan.

43:05.840 --> 43:07.670
His feelings for her now are complex.

43:08.360 --> 43:09.750
If you kill her now,

43:10.320 --> 43:11.580
it will only make him

43:12.030 --> 43:14.380
more determined to fight against you.

43:17.230 --> 43:18.960
You have a better idea?

43:20.400 --> 43:21.810
Let him rescue Wu Wangyan,

43:22.760 --> 43:23.850
let them rekindle their bond,

43:24.220 --> 43:25.390
let their feelings grow deeper.

43:25.880 --> 43:27.420
Once he gathers all the Dragon Deity's Power

43:28.030 --> 43:29.610
and his love for her runs deep,

43:30.150 --> 43:32.170
I'll kill Wu Wangyan before his eyes.

43:35.440 --> 43:36.570
He'll surely break down then.

43:45.670 --> 43:47.740
You can take the chance

43:47.920 --> 43:48.980
to seize his body.

43:50.320 --> 43:51.650
Then go to the Dragon Abyss,

43:52.320 --> 43:53.300
kill Chi Wen,

43:54.510 --> 43:55.770
and free your true form

43:56.510 --> 43:57.440
from within his body.

43:59.850 --> 44:00.460
What do you think?

44:02.770 --> 44:03.750
And you?

44:06.960 --> 44:08.180
What do you want?

44:14.750 --> 44:16.950
I want to remain the Dragon Deity.

44:29.340 --> 44:30.500
♪It's your light♪

44:30.700 --> 44:32.580
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

44:32.740 --> 44:35.860
♪That set the night alight♪

44:36.220 --> 44:42.740
♪And lead me through the fight♪

44:44.500 --> 44:46.380
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

44:46.820 --> 44:51.260
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

44:52.060 --> 44:53.740
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

44:53.900 --> 44:59.300
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

45:00.060 --> 45:05.460
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

45:07.780 --> 45:13.820
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

45:14.780 --> 45:16.940
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

45:17.220 --> 45:22.060
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

45:22.420 --> 45:24.740
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

45:24.940 --> 45:30.020
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

45:30.260 --> 45:32.260
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

45:32.540 --> 45:36.900
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

45:37.900 --> 45:44.860
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

46:01.420 --> 46:04.380
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

46:05.460 --> 46:08.860
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

46:09.660 --> 46:12.180
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

46:12.420 --> 46:15.500
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

46:15.900 --> 46:18.220
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

46:18.740 --> 46:23.140
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

46:23.380 --> 46:25.540
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

46:25.940 --> 46:30.900
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

46:31.140 --> 46:32.300
♪It's your light♪

46:32.500 --> 46:34.340
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

46:34.540 --> 46:37.660
♪That set the night alight♪

46:38.420 --> 46:47.860
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
